---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | Make Your Own Tools"
  description="Affiliate disclosure for Make Your Own Tools, explaining how product recommendations and outbound affiliate links may support the site."
  canonical="/affiliate-disclosure/"
>
  <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-6 py-12 md:px-8 md:py-16">
    <a href="/" class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-zinc-300 transition hover:border-white/30 hover:bg-white/10">
      <span>←</span>
      <span>Home</span>
    </a>

    <article class="glass-shell-strong rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-9">
      <p class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-amber-300/30 bg-amber-300/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-amber-100">
        Monetization Transparency
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300">
        Make Your Own Tools may earn a commission when you click a product link and make a purchase. This does not change your price, and it helps fund hosting, maintenance, testing, and new calculators.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-7 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-300">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">How Recommendations Are Chosen</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Product recommendations should connect to the calculator result or planning scenario on the page, such as a battery capacity range, solar panel size, NAS disk count, or infrastructure deployment need.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Editorial Independence</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Affiliate availability does not guarantee a product will be recommended. The site should prioritize practical compatibility, clear tradeoffs, and user intent over the highest possible commission.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Future Affiliate Programs</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Potential categories include solar panels, LiFePO4 batteries, charge controllers, NAS drives, UPS units, server hardware, VPS providers, and cloud infrastructure tools.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">User Responsibility</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Calculator outputs and product ranges are planning aids, not a substitute for reading manufacturer specifications, local electrical rules, warranty terms, or safety documentation. Before buying or installing hardware, confirm voltage, current, connector type, enclosure rating, thermal limits, and compatibility with your existing system.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Clear Labeling</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">When an outbound recommendation is an affiliate link, the surrounding page should make that relationship clear. The goal is to keep monetization visible, understandable, and secondary to the usefulness of the calculator result.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
